actionConfiguration.body: SELECT * FROM plants ORDER BY "internal_ingredient_ID" LIMIT 10 offset {{(Table_Plants.pageNo - 1) * 10}};;
SELECT * FROM plants ORDER BY "internal_ingredient_ID" LIMIT 10 offset {{(Table_Plants.pageNo - 1) * 10}};;

UPDATE public."plants" SET
  "Scientific Justification - Bioactive" = '{{Input_Sci_Justification_Bioact.text}}',
  "Scientific Justification - Functionality" = '{{Input_Sci_Justification_Functi.text}}',
  "Scientific Justification - Taxonomy" = '{{Input_Sci_Justification_Taxono.text}}',
  "Scientific Explantion - Molecular" = '{{Input_Sci_Justification_Molecu.text}}'
  WHERE "internal_ingredient_ID" = {{ Table_Plants.selectedRow.internal_ingredient_ID }};
